# 🚀 Jibon EV – Smart Electric Scooter Rental Platform

Jibon EV is a modern web platform for renting electric scooters, inspired by real-world services like Zepto delivery mobility systems.

---  

## 🌟 Features

* ⚡ EV scooter booking systems
* 💰 Pricing calculator
* 📱 Fully responsive design (mobile + desktop) 
* 🔐 User signup & validation
* 🎯 Smooth animations & modern UI
* 🧭 Easy navigation system
 
---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

* Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
* Backend: Node.js, Express.js
* Database: MongoDB


---

## 🌐 Live Demo

👉 https://jibonelectric.com

---

## ⚙️ How to Run this project

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusernam/jibon-ev.git
cd jibon-ev
npm install
npm start
```

